,"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26649","headword_ar":"اِطَّرَقَ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 3. Said of the wing of a bird, (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its feathers overlay one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, abundant and dense"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its feathers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AT~rqt AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"اطّرقت الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The earth became disposed in layers, one above another, being compacted by the rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AT~rq","text_ar":"اطّرق"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawoDu","text_ar":"الحَوْضُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The watering-trough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tank, had in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a deposit of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compacted dung,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dung and mud"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clay, that had fallen into it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AT~rq Ealayohi All~ayolu","text_ar":"اطّرق عَلَيْهِ اللَّيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the O and L; in the K, erroneously, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraqa","text_ar":"اَطْرَقَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night came upon him portion upon portion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also 6, in three places."}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26673","headword_ar":"اَطْرَقُ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the affection termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tariqa","text_ar":"طَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqaA='u","text_ar":"طَرْقَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K:) and the latter is said by Lth to be applied to the hind leg as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the crookedness termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraqN","text_ar":"طَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAq","text_ar":"سَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}